summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1567, for the improvement of 9th Avenue West from West Prospect Street to West Lee Street, and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues all in the City of Seattle by grading and re-grading the same, and by constructing concrete sidewalks thereon, under Ordinance No. 16787 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
